<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Admin Login</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #efe8dc;
      --panel: rgba(255, 250, 242, 0.9);
      --ink: #1d2a2f;
      --muted: #66757e;
      --brand: #0f766e;
      --brand-deep: #0b4f49;
      --danger: #b42318;
      --line: rgba(29, 42, 47, 0.12);
      --shadow: 0 30px 70px rgba(30, 41, 46, 0.16);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: 24px;
      font-family: "Avenir Next", "Helvetica Neue", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.18), transparent 24%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(180, 35, 24, 0.1), transparent 18%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f7f1e6 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
    }

    .shell {
      width: min(980px, 100%);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      border-radius: 30px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    }

    .intro {
      padding: 48px;
      background: linear-gradient(150deg, rgba(11, 79, 73, 0.96), rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.9));
      color: #f8fafc;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 36px;
    }

    .intro h1 {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: clamp(38px, 5vw, 58px);
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .intro p {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 420px;
      color: rgba(241, 245, 249, 0.82);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      opacity: 0.76;
    }

    .notes {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .note {
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.82);
    }

    .panel {
      padding: 42px;
      background: var(--panel);
    }

    .panel h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .panel p {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    form {
      margin-top: 28px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    label {
      display: grid;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #304047;
    }

    input {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 50px;
      padding: 0 14px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.94);
      color: var(--ink);
      font: inherit;
    }

    input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.5);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.12);
    }

    .error {
      padding: 13px 14px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(180, 35, 24, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(180, 35, 24, 0.14);
      color: var(--danger);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .btn {
      min-height: 52px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), #115e59);
      color: #fff;
      font: inherit;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 34px rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.22);
    }

    .footnote {
      margin-top: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px) {
      .shell { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .intro, .panel { padding: 28px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="shell">
    <section class="intro">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">Protected Access</div>
        <h1>iMD Admin</h1>
        <p>Sign in to manage package uploads, quarantine invalid archives, and open the internal dashboard without exposing broken content to the app.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="notes">
        <div class="note">Valid package folders are now separated from broken imports automatically.</div>
        <div class="note">Zip and folder uploads are checked for supported structure before they appear in the library.</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel">
      <h2>Sign in</h2>
      <p>Use the configured admin credentials to continue to the dashboard.</p>

      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="error"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>

      <form action="/login" method="POST">
        <input type="hidden" name="next" value="<%= nextPath || '/dashboard' %>">
        <label>
          Username
          <input type="text" name="username" value="<%= username || '' %>" autocomplete="username" required>
        </label>
        <label>
          Password
          <input type="password" name="password" autocomplete="current-password" required>
        </label>
        <button class="btn" type="submit">Open Dashboard</button>
      </form>

      <div class="footnote">First run defaults are username <strong>admin</strong> and password <strong>admin123</strong>. After signing in, you can change the username, password, and cookie secret from the dashboard.</div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>